    "Think about previous vehicles owned": "\"I have owned three Mazdas in my life. It was the first car I owned and I drove it into the ground. It never gave me any problems, it was great.\"\r\n\r\n\"I love Mazdas. My last Mazda I had for 11 years. I really didn't want to get a new car, but we have a new grandson and need more space. I knew straight away I was getting another Mazda. \"",
